Chords is a responsive web app supporting user authentication.
Users can view and send song lyrics, guitar chords and tabs.

***This site is under heavy development!***

Requires/uses
--------------
requires: python3, django (tested with 1.8 version only)
required apps: django-registration-redux, django-password-validation
uses: html5, jquery, bootstrap

Get started
------------
Make migrations:
`./manage.py makemigrations chords`
`./manage.py migrate`

Populate some test data (optional):
`./populate_chords.py`

Create a superuser for the admin site (optional):
`./manage.py createsuperuser`

Run the development server:
`./manage.py runserver`

You can now visit the site on http://localhost:8000/chords/.
